{"tid":627414,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"九龍塘站助理染腦膜炎","createTime":"2018-04-13T03:13:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-13T03:15:11.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e838da88722ca8c98f50095bb576edf8b403d6f9","tid":627414,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T03:13:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180413/20360022?_ga=2.40608674.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180413%2F20360022%3F_ga%3D2.40608674.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&d=0oCxB4PKUF1ZroO7ywWN2P755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=f01f9e7c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180413%2F20360022%3F_ga%3D2.40608674.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&h=818df95e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180413/20360022?_ga=2.40608674.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171</a><br />\n<br />\n九龍塘站助理染腦膜炎<br />\n<br />\n3.3K<br />\n港聞<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180413/large/17344865.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180413%2Flarge%2F17344865.jpg&h=6a90af23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九龍塘站一名月台助理感染侵入性腦膜炎雙球菌，目前情況危殆。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】港鐵九龍塘站一名曾近距離接觸乘客的月台助理，證實感染可經飛沫傳播的侵入性腦膜炎雙球菌，於周日病發後入住廣華醫院深切治療部接受治療，目前情況危殆。港鐵已用漂白水為九龍塘站進行緊急清潔消毒。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵昨日凌晨公佈，一名在九龍塘站工作的月台助理被確診感染腦膜炎雙球菌。港鐵已即時按照衞生防護中心指引制訂的既定程序，安排清潔員工以1:49濃度的漂白水為九龍塘站進行清潔消毒，並已安排加強相關地方的通風隔塵網清洗。港鐵亦已要求車站其他員工如身體出現發燒、咳嗽等病徵，應盡快求診，並知會其上司。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n病菌可經飛沫傳播<br />\n<br />\n據衞生防護中心公佈的資料，受感染的港鐵月台助理是一名有長期病患的60歲男子，他自4月8日起出現發燒、咳嗽和四肢乏力，翌日入住廣華醫院，其後被轉往深切治療部接受進一步治療，現時情況危殆。<br />\n<br />\n病人的血液樣本經化驗後，證實對腦膜炎雙球菌呈陽性反應。初步調查顯示，病人近期沒有外遊，其家居接觸者至今沒有出現病徵。衞生防護中心解釋，腦膜炎雙球菌感染主要經由接觸帶菌者的飛沫傳播，潛伏期由2至10日，一般為3至4日。病徵包括發燒、劇烈頭痛、皮膚出現瘀斑、頸部僵硬等。若情況嚴重更可造成腦部損害或死亡。<br />\n<br />\n■記者麥志榮"},{"pid":"36613ff908435fc7cbc359d698786794a2a90eae","tid":627414,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T03:15:11.000Z","msg":"樓主硬膠泛民打手LIKLN都應該有腦膜炎<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/09/191003_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F09%2F191003_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=3124d977&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/09/191008_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F09%2F191008_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=ff15f2d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/10/201929_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F10%2F201929_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=27225035&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}